          <p class="fragment">It's a platform that makes deployments easy. <br>Tradionally this was hard.</p>
          <br>
          <p class="fragment">Heroku lets app developers spend 100% of their time on their application code, not managing servers, deployment, ongoing operations, or scaling.</p>
